<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Welcome to Amebo Naija</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7f4;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #16a34a;
      padding: 40px 40px 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .header .logo span {
      color: #bbf7d0;
    }

    .header .tagline {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #bbf7d0;
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15803d 0%, #16a34a 50%, #22c55e 100%);
      padding: 36px 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero .emoji {
      font-size: 48px;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      color: #bbf7d0;
    }

    .body {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .body p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .body p strong {
      color: #16a34a;
    }

    .features {
      background-color: #f0fdf4;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #16a34a;
    }

    .features p.label {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #16a34a;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .feature-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 18px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .feature-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .feature-text strong {
      color: #15803d;
      display: block;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cta-wrapper {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0 8px;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #16a34a;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 14px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.35);
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: #e5e7eb;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 28px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .footer p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .footer a {
      color: #16a34a;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .footer .social {
      margin: 14px 0 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Amebo<span>Naija</span></div>
      <div class="tagline">Nigeria's #1 Gist Hub</div>
    </div>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
      <span class="emoji"></span>
      <h1>Welcome aboard, <span><%= firstName %>!</span></h1>
    </div>

    <!-- BODY -->
    <div class="body">
      <p>
        We're so excited to have you join the <strong>Amebo Naija</strong> family — the place where the hottest gist, news, entertainment, sports, and lifestyle content in Nigeria lives!
      </p>

      <p>
        Your account is all set up and ready to go. Here's everything you can do on the platform:
      </p>

      <div class="features">
        <p class="label">What you can do</p>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">✍️</span>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <strong>Write & Share Posts</strong>
            Submit your own gist, news, and stories for the community to read
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">📰</span>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <strong>Read the Latest Gist</strong>
            Stay up to date with news, gossip, entertainment, sports & lifestyle
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">💬</span>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <strong>Join the Conversation</strong>
            Comment, like and share posts that move you
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">🔥</span>
          <div class="feature-text">
            <strong>Trending Content</strong>
            Discover what Nigerians are talking about right now
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you ever have questions or need help, feel free to reach out to us. We're always here for you.
      </p>

      <p>
        Now go ahead — explore, read, and drop your gist! 🇳🇬
      </p>

      <div class="cta-wrapper">
        <a href="https://amebonaija.com" class="cta-btn">
          Start Exploring →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        If you didn't create an account on Amebo Naija, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social">🇳🇬</div>
      <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Amebo Naija. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        You're receiving this email because you just signed up on
        <a href="https://amebonaija.vercel.app">amebonaija.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>